update.name: CVE-2024-3094-Vulnerability-Checker-Fixer
update.description: This project contains a shell script designed to help users identify and fix installations of xz-utils affected by the CVE-2024-3094 vulnerability. Versions 5.6.0 and 5.6.1 of xz-utils are known to be vulnerable, and this script aids in detecting them and optionally downgrading to a stable, un-compromised version (5.4.6).
